@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_coxata(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 0.53
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.59) / ((v1 + 0.04 * tmp + 0.16) / (tmp + 0.43 + v2 + 0.53)))
    v1 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.53 / v1 + 0.69)) / v1)
    tmp = wp.abs(v0)
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.83) + (v2 + 0.69 + v2 + 0.52)) - wp.sin((v1 + 0.89 * v0 + 0.17)))
    data[tid] = v0
